What you need to know:  Tuwei said that they have started early preparations ahead of the competition and he believes a strong team will be selected during the junior trials that will be held from July 8 to 9The camp hosts 15 youths from Kakuma Refugee Camp and 55 from the Kapsumbeiywo CampJepkosgei is confident that a good number of athletes from the camp will make it to Team Kenya for the junior championships in August